---
import brechaData from '../../data/B1/bloque_1_brecha_informativa.json'
import metodosData from '../../data/B1/bloque_1_metodos_extraccion.json'
import B1DonutMetodos from '../../components/charts/B1DonutMetodos'

const totalRegistros = brechaData.total_registros.toLocaleString('es-PE')
const unknownCount = brechaData.unknown_count.toLocaleString('es-PE')
const knownCount = brechaData.known_count.toLocaleString('es-PE')
const unknownPct = brechaData.unknown_pct
const knownPct = brechaData.known_pct

const knownMethods = metodosData.filter((d) => d.method !== 'Unknown')
const totalKnown = knownMethods.reduce((sum, d) => sum + d.frequency, 0)
---

<section class="b1-section w-[80%] mx-auto border border-white/20">
  <div class="b1-inner">
    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="b1-header">
      <span class="b1-badge">BLOQUE 01 · EXTRACCIÓN</span>
      <h2 class="b1-title">Métodos de Extracción Minera</h2>
      <p class="b1-subtitle">
        ¿Qué sabemos realmente sobre cómo se extrae en el Perú? La mayoría de sitios mineros
        carecen de información sobre su método de extracción. Aquí exploramos tanto la brecha
        informativa como la distribución de los métodos identificados.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Two-column layout: cards left, chart right -->
    <div class="b1-content">
      <!-- Left column: stat cards -->
      <div class="b1-cards">
        <!-- Card: Total -->
        <div class="b1-card b1-card--total">
          <div class="b1-card__number b1-card__number--hero">{totalRegistros}</div>
          <div class="b1-card__label">Sitios mineros registrados</div>
          <div class="b1-card__desc">
            Total de registros en la base de datos del sector minero peruano analizados en este
            estudio.
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card: Desconocido -->
        <div class="b1-card b1-card--unknown">
          <div class="b1-card__pct">{unknownPct}%</div>
          <div class="b1-card__number">{unknownCount}</div>
          <div class="b1-card__label">Sin método identificado</div>
          <div class="b1-card__bar">
            <div
              class="b1-card__bar-fill b1-card__bar-fill--unknown"
              style={`width: ${unknownPct}%`}
            >
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="b1-card__desc">
            Más de tres cuartas partes de los sitios mineros carecen de información sobre su método
            de extracción.
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card: Conocido -->
        <div class="b1-card b1-card--known">
          <div class="b1-card__pct">{knownPct}%</div>
          <div class="b1-card__number">{knownCount}</div>
          <div class="b1-card__label">Con método identificado</div>
          <div class="b1-card__bar">
            <div
              class="b1-card__bar-fill b1-card__bar-fill--known"
              style={`width: ${knownPct}%`}
            >
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="b1-card__desc">
            Solo una fracción menor cuenta con datos sobre si la operación es subterránea, a tajo
            abierto o mixta.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right column: donut chart -->
      <div class="b1-chart-wrapper">
        <B1DonutMetodos data={metodosData} client:only="react" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Unified insight -->
    <div class="b1-insight">
      <span class="b1-insight__icon">⚠</span>
      <p class="b1-insight__text">
        De los <strong>{totalRegistros}</strong> sitios registrados, el
        <strong>{unknownPct}%</strong> no tiene método de extracción clasificado — una brecha que
        condiciona todo el análisis. De los
        <strong>{totalKnown.toLocaleString('es-PE')}</strong> sitios con información disponible, la
        minería subterránea lidera con amplio margen. Las conclusiones sobre distribución geográfica,
        relación mineral-método y escala operativa se basan únicamente en ese
        <strong>{knownPct}%</strong> de registros con datos completos.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .b1-section {
    padding: 80px 0 60px;
    background: var(--bg-primary);
  }

  .b1-inner {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 32px;
  }

  /* Header */
  .b1-header {
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .b1-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.625rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--accent-lime);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    padding: 4px 14px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(193, 214, 91, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(193, 214, 91, 0.15);
  }

  .b1-title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  }

  .b1-subtitle {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.65;
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Two-column content */
  .b1-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .b1-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.4fr;
      align-items: stretch;
    }
  }

  /* Left column: stat cards stack */
  .b1-cards {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  /* Cards */
  .b1-card {
    position: relative;
    padding: 22px 20px;
    background: var(--glass-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
    overflow: hidden;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .b1-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
  }

  .b1-card__pct {
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
  }

  .b1-card__number {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  }

  .b1-card__number--hero {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    letter-spacing: -1px;
  }

  .b1-card__label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.8px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .b1-card__desc {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* Progress bar */
  .b1-card__bar {
    width: 100%;
    height: 4px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .b1-card__bar-fill {
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: width 0.8s ease;
  }

  /* Card: Unknown */
  .b1-card--unknown .b1-card__pct {
    color: var(--accent-brown-light);
  }

  .b1-card--unknown .b1-card__number {
    color: var(--accent-brown);
  }

  .b1-card__bar-fill--unknown {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent-brown), var(--accent-brown-light));
  }

  /* Card: Known */
  .b1-card--known .b1-card__pct {
    color: var(--accent-lime-light);
  }

  .b1-card--known .b1-card__number {
    color: var(--accent-lime);
  }

  .b1-card__bar-fill--known {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent-lime), var(--accent-lime-light));
  }

  /* Right column: chart wrapper */
  .b1-chart-wrapper {
    padding: 24px;
    background: var(--glass-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    min-height: 420px;
  }

  .b1-chart-wrapper :global(> div) {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  /* Insight */
  .b1-insight {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    background: rgba(132, 98, 72, 0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(132, 98, 72, 0.15);
  }

  .b1-insight__icon {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .b1-insight__text {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .b1-insight__text strong {
    color: var(--accent-lime-light);
  }
</style>
